## 🔄 状态管理

### 本地状态
```typescript
// ✅ 推荐：使用 useState 和 useCallback
function UserForm() {
  const [formData, setFormData] = useState<UserFormData>({
    name: '',
    email: '',
  });
  
  const handleSubmit = useCallback(async () => {
    try {
      await submitUser(formData);
      message.success('保存成功');
    } catch (error) {
      message.error('保存失败');
    }
  }, [formData]);
}
```

